1. **Streamlit UI Singularity（單一 UI 樞紐）:** `rs_manager.py` IS PERMANENTLY DEPRECATED. All CEO interactions (pipeline triggers, vault management, regeneration) MUST go through the Streamlit Web UI (Tab1-6). Never re-implement CLI wrappers.

